original_query: How much money did Anmol Singh paid to DLF indirectly to buy an apartment? Search Local documents only.
summarizer_summary: Funds originating from Gensol Engineering Limited, which included a loan from IREDA, were transferred via Capbridge and Jasminder Kaur to DLF as part of the consideration (Rs. 42.94 Crore) for the purchase of an apartment in 'The Camellias' project.
